snippet.title: DRAGON BALL Z: KAKAROT - Character Progression Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Battling foes, training with friends, and eating meals are some of the many ways you can grow your character in DRAGON BALL Z: KAKAROT! 

Be the hope of the universe when DRAGON BALL: KAKAROT releases on January 17, 2020! 

https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP0700-CUSA14655_00-NEWDBZRPG0000000
